# P3-EXT002: AdaptiveContrastEffect — Specification

## What This Module Does

Adaptive contrast stretching with local detail enhancement, inspired by Mutable Instruments Streams audio dynamics processor. The effect analyzes local neighborhoods in the image to automatically stretch luminance ranges, lifting shadows and crushing highlights while preserving detail. Unlike global contrast adjustment, this adapts to local brightness variations, revealing detail in both dark and bright areas simultaneously.

**Core Innovation:** Audio dynamics concepts (compression, expansion, local vs global processing) translated to image processing. The `locality` parameter controls the analysis window size, creating a spectrum from global auto-level to highly localized contrast enhancement.

